    <IRI>https://www.argumentum.games/argumentum_virtues.owl#hanlonsRazor</IRI>
    <Literal xml:lang="EN">Interpretive principle consisting in not attributing to malice what can reasonably be explained by incompetence or ignorance.</Literal>
