    <IRI>https://www.argumentum.games/argumentum_virtues.owl#rigorousConstructionOfStatements</IRI>
    <Literal xml:lang="EN">Development of logically coherent and structured statements with valid syntax in a clearly identified logical system.</Literal>
  </AnnotationAssertion>
