    <IRI>https://www.argumentum.games/argumentum_virtues.owl#inference:ReductioAdAbsurdum</IRI>
    <Literal xml:lang="EN">Demonstrative technique that establishes the truth of a proposition by showing that its opposite leads to absurdity.</Literal>
